summary: This document is a certification from the State of New York Department of State regarding the filing of Articles of Organization for NES, LLC, a limited liability company. It notes that the company is existing according to the records, but its Biennial Statement is past due.

persons.name: Anthony Giardina
persons.context: Anthony Giardina certifies the existence of NES, LLC and signs the document as the Executive Deputy Secretary of State.

keyFacts: NES, LLC was filed as a New York Limited Liability Company on 08/13/1998.
The Biennial Statement for NES, LLC is past due.
The document is certified by Anthony Giardina, Executive Deputy Secretary of State.
